    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>soy sauce</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with your<strong> honey</strong>, <strong>chilli relish</strong> and 30ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[45ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [60ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1630485845903-x200.jpg",
