            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>salmon fillet[s]</strong>, skin-side down, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the skin has started to crisp</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1630485849486-x200.jpg",
