      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, add your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> to the pan with the salmon – this is your<strong> sweet chilli salmon</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if your sauce is looking a little thick!</p>",
      "order": 7,
